dataIdInfo.idPurp:
Bessemer City Zoning Districts and Overlays for analysis and planning purposes.
Updated 02.04.2025
dataIdInfo.idAbs:
Bessemer City Land Use Code represents the zoning regulations within the City of Bessemer and the ETJ Extra Territorial Jurisdiction. This data is represented by data provided by the municipal jurisdiction but does not replace the official zoning map of the jurisdiction, please verify the zoning information with that jurisdiction.

This data is updated upon notification from the Town or City upon a board approved action of rezoning, annexation or other board action.
